### Alle To-Do-Listen abrufen
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lists
Accept: application/json

###

### Einzelne To-Do-Liste abrufen
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lists/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Alle Tasks einer bestimmten Liste abrufen (Response ohne listId)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lists/1/tasks
Accept: application/json

###

### Neue To-Do-Liste erstellen
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lists
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Work-{{$timestamp}}",
  "description": "Liste fuer Tasks-{{$timestamp}}"
}

